{"tid":2137562,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"（高質燒腦追兇韓劇）十匙一飯","createTime":"2020-08-03T04:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T04:43:48.000Z","uid":224375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7a7bd20eb937d468731c4a61ecdd0fc801e8737a","tid":2137562,"uid":224375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T04:36:33.000Z","msg":"韓劇《十匙一飯》又譯《United Effort to Accomplish One Thing》，接檔《一起吃晚飯嗎》，於每週三、四晚間各播放一集。<br />\n《十匙一飯》劇名源於韓國一句成語，意思是「十湯匙就能湊齊一碗飯，只要每個人都付出一些微薄之力，就能幫助一個人」。 故事從一名擁有600億韓元資產的名畫家死亡開始，畫家的遺屬與辦案人員聚集在他的豪宅裡，一場勾心鬥角的對決就此展開，旨在描述人們在貪念萌發當下做出的各種選擇。<br />\n<br />\n電視台：MBC電視臺 出品時間：2020年07月15日 集數：8集<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1PhiQsq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1PhiQsq.jpg&h=90281748&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Psv8td6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPsv8td6.jpg&h=91da4ef2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32d22656dbb8411322bf9df67eb004da305b754f","tid":2137562,"uid":107913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T04:41:44.000Z","msg":"好似話同Knives Out電影差唔多....."},{"pid":"5c463e1dab2a3ac9f68907723118b6b059096ce1","tid":2137562,"uid":224375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T04:43:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3z6-U2UEfjs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3z6-U2UEfjs&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2FyrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=55a66f93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3z6-U2UEfjs</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇到第三集，好唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}